snippet.title: Gta 5 Turn off Cops in Story mode / offline single
snippet.description:
Hey what's up you guyz, if you wonder is there any way to get cops off in Gta V, just play flawlessly in your own style(Rampage maybe)? 

Yeah that's possible if you could enter the cool function that built in the game called "Director mode". So here im gonna show you the way of doing that on PC version which will also work in consoles.

Rare Bikes Locations(Can't Buy):
▫️Dinka Double-T - https://bit.ly/36E0nww
▫️Shitzu Hakuchou - https://bit.ly/38fK8WO
▫️Principe Nemesis - https://bit.ly/3vhTpqN
▫️Dinka Thrust - https://bit.ly/3rLsp0i
▫️Western Daemon - https://bit.ly/3LbaiZr

▫️SuperCar Locations in Story Mode - https://bit.ly/3MrhnFD

►Leaving a LIKE would always appreciate! 
►Subscribe for latest video uploads! http://bit.ly/29ZRld9

Our social media :
◽Like on Facebook: http://bit.ly/2acp9pO
◽Follow on Twitter: http://bit.ly/6zco6Xb
◽Message on Hangouts: RoaringDroidLine 

Notice: 
◽This feature works on Xbox One, PlayStation 4, and PC.
◽PlayStation 3 or Xbox 360 won't have this option.
◽This mode can be enabled at anytime except during a mission  and all the functions are working as long as you stay there.
◽You can't collect any money, weapon, ammo and skills which will not be improved. 
◽If you get wasted, you will be ended up at hospital, not at casting trailer. (will also disable the mode)

Thanks for watching and see you next time!
